OL,3,CWater firms ratings at record low as
OL,4,Csewage pollution surges
OL,6,FWater companies in England have
OL,7,Freceived their worst environmental
OL,8,Fperformance ratings since records
OL,9,Fbegan, with Southern Water and Thames
OL,10,FWater among the most heavily
OL,11,Fcriticised for sewage pollution.
OL,13,FThe latest Environment Agency (EA)
OL,14,Fassessment shows firms scored just 19
OL,15,Fout of a possible 36 stars in 2024,
OL,16,Fdown from 25 the year before.
OL,18,FSerious incidents, which are those
OL,19,Fclassed as causing significant
OL,20,Fenvironmental harm, have increased by
OL,21,F60% compared with 2023.
