OL,3,CWater firms ratings at record low as
OL,4,Csewage pollution surges
OL,6,FOnly Severn Trent achieved full marks,
OL,7,Fwith Thames Water the only company
OL,8,Fawarded just one star, amid its
OL,9,Fongoing financial uncertainty.
OL,11,FSouthern Water, was handed a two star
OL,12,Frating, meaning it "requires
OL,13,Fimprovement" after causing 269
OL,14,Fpollution incidents last year,
OL,15,Fincluding 15 classed as serious.
OL,17,FTogether with Yorkshire Water, these 3
OL,18,Fcompanies were responsible for more
OL,19,Fthan 80% of serious pollution
OL,20,Fincidents last year.
