OL,3,CWater firms ratings at record low as
OL,4,Csewage pollution surges
OL,6,FEA chair Alan Lovell said the findings
OL,7,Fwere "poor" and must be a "clear and
OL,8,Furgent signal for change." He is
OL,9,Fcalling for "bold leadership, a shift
OL,10,Fin mindset and a relentless focus on
OL,11,Fdelivery."
OL,13,FDawn Theaker, the EA's water
OL,14,Fregulation manager for the South, said
OL,15,FSouthern Water needed to "get a grip"
OL,16,Fon its pollution record, adding:
OL,17,F"Everyone wants Southern Water to
OL,18,Fimprove. And it can."
