OL,3,CWater firms ratings at record low as
OL,4,Csewage pollution surges
OL,6,FSouthern Water's CEO, Lawrence Gosden,
OL,7,Fsaid: "These reports draw on data from
OL,8,Flast year, and as far back as January
OL,9,F2024.
OL,11,F"We acknowledge that our regulators
OL,12,Fwant to see our performance improve,
OL,13,Fand we share that ambition. But we're
OL,14,Fmaking clear progress in many areas `
OL,15,Fso the reports out today don't tell
OL,16,Fthe whole story.
