OL,3,CWater firms ratings at record low as
OL,4,Csewage pollution surges
OL,6,F"With the commitment of our amazing
OL,7,Fpeople and the strong support of our
OL,8,Fshareholder, all of us at Southern
OL,9,FWater are determined to serve our
OL,10,Fcustomers and the environment better --
OL,11,F and we're on track to achieve that."
OL,13,FITV News Meridian has approached
OL,14,FThames Water for comment.
OL,16,FThe report blames the wet and stormy
OL,17,Fweather in 2024, underinvestment and
OL,18,Fpoor maintenance of infrastructure,
OL,19,Fand also increased monitoring and
OL,20,Finspection, for the decrease in
OL,21,Fperformance.
